name: 404 Not Found
description:
The number 404 Not Found is an error message, but in Indonesia it is a scary message. Last August, an artist created a mural with the words "404 not found" on a face that looks like the Indonesian president. 

The news seems to be being discussed a lot in Indonesia.
Initially the police were going to process the artist, but in the end the artist apologized so the Police have confirmed that they will not process it.

“This shows that the government is increasingly anti-criticism, be it murals, tweets, or t-shirt designs.


As long as we make a mural that contains criticism and not insults, we don't have to worry
